OL,3,CMan caught on camera stealing gas
OL,4,Ccanisters jailed three days later
OL,6,FA thief from Ashford who stole from a
OL,7,Flocal business has been arrested,
OL,8,Fcharged, and sentenced to jail less
OL,9,Fthan three days after his crimes.
OL,11,FAt midday on Saturday 17 January, 43-
OL,12,Fyear-old Daniel Hilden drove to a
OL,13,Fbusiness in Ashford.
OL,15,FCCTV captured him breaking a padlock,
OL,16,Fentering a business premises, and then
OL,17,Fdriving away.
