OL,3,CMan caught on camera stealing gas
OL,4,Ccanisters jailed three days later
OL,6,FA few hours later, Hilden returned and
OL,7,Fforced entry into a locked storage
OL,8,Fcage, removing several gas canisters
OL,9,Fbefore fleeing the scene.
OL,11,FHilden returned for a final time at
OL,12,F6pm the following day to steal further
OL,13,Fgas canisters from the same secure
OL,14,Fstorage area.
OL,16,FIn total, Hilden stole almost #1,000
OL,17,Fworth of property.
