OL,3,CMan caught on camera stealing gas
OL,4,Ccanisters jailed three days later
OL,6,FNeighbourhood Policing officers
OL,7,Freviewed the CCTV on the morning of
OL,8,FMonday 19 January and immediately
OL,9,Fidentified Hilden.
OL,11,FBy 10.15, officers had arrested him
OL,12,Foutside his home and he was charged
OL,13,Fwith burglary the same evening.
OL,15,FHilden, of Steddy Close, Ashford,
OL,16,Fappeared at Margate Magistrates' Court
OL,17,Fthe next day (Tuesday 20 January),
OL,18,Fwhere he pleaded guilty and was
OL,19,Fimmediately sentenced to eight months'
OL,20,Fimprisonment.
