OL,3,CMan caught on camera stealing gas
OL,4,Ccanisters jailed three days later
OL,6,FA 17-year-old alleged accomplice was
OL,7,Falso arrested in connection with the
OL,8,Fincident and is due to appear before
OL,9,FFolkestone Youth Court on 3 February.
OL,11,FDetective Inspector Simon Johnson
OL,12,Fsaid: "Thanks to the strong local
OL,13,Fknowledge of our officers, we have
OL,14,Fbeen able to rapidly bring this
OL,15,Fburglar to justice.
OL,17,F"This case shows the importance of
OL,18,Fneighbourhood police officers, who
OL,19,Fknow their patch and can take action
OL,20,Fagainst offenders to protect
OL,21,Fbusinesses and residents."
